         Mezzed PC's or NPC's won't get attacked by a pet when the mez spell hits them. But if they are mezzed and you command the pet to attack the mezzed PC or NPC it will attack as normal. It will work only to wipe NPC's that get mezzed from pets agro list. Other interest thing i saw on the Dev board is that if the mob is mezzed and the pet is casting a spell on it, it WILL break the mez.</P><P>Onail Aeroc<BR>49 Necromancer<BR>Aei'Desis for life<BR>Xegony</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
